<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٦٤٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5243">قَيْسُ بْنُ حَفْصٍ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1717">خَالِدُ بْنُ الْحَارِثِ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7060">أَبِي التَّيَّاحِ </a>قَالَ سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ <span class="c2">«الْخَيْلُ مَعْقُودٌ فِي نَوَاصِيهَا الْخَيْرُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>